story *
once upon a time, there was a monkey who lived in the banks of a river.The mokey would goto collect fruits for him everyday.in the same river there lived a crocodile who became good friends with the monkey.One day the crocodile's wife requested the crocodile to bring the monkey to their house for a dinner and instead of giving him food they would eat his heart because she thought that his heart would be very tasty as he eats good fruits all day.Another day the monkey came to their house and when the crocodile's wife told him their plan he came up with an excuse that he left his heart in the tree and requested the crocodile to take him back to the tree so that he can bring his heart.  